{"tid":2131903,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"死熱狗 自2014年開始老屈 肥佬黎","createTime":"2020-07-30T06:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T07:04:27.000Z","uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b621015c56004fe6efd4e9772b510f6fdd7c5831","tid":2131903,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:36:40.000Z","msg":"黎智英認封殺本土派 作者：熱血編輯部 (Thomas Tsang) 07-25-2014 313 0 0 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201407/%E9%BB%8E%E6%99%BA%E8%8B%B1%E8%AA%8D%E5%B0%81%E6%AE%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%9F%E6%B4%BE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201407%2F%25E9%25BB%258E%25E6%2599%25BA%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%25B0%2581%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%259F%25E6%25B4%25BE.jpg&h=9421551e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒集團主席黎智英今日在其網台節目《壹錘定音》中表示，中港不能分割，自己及壹傳媒的立場均是反對「港獨」，更自爆封殺本土派言論。<br />\n<br />\n 《人民日報》海外版昨日發表文章，指斥黎智英「禍港亂港、支持台獨」。黎智英表示從未支持台獨，亦覺得現時情況台灣是不可能獨立。 <br />\n<br />\n被問及對「港獨」的睇法時，黎智英認為香港根本永遠不能和中國分割，支持港獨是「戇居」的，現時只是在「兩制」下進行抗爭。黎又承認曾對集團高層發出內部通知，禁止旗下刊物及報章容許支持本土化的人士發表太多言論，以防被中共視為支持「港獨」，使壹傳媒遭到全面封殺。 <br />\n<br />\n黎智英更直言<span class=\"red\">「港獨」是一個陰謀，最終目的是打擊泛民主派及民主運動</span>。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-25-2014/18043\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F07-25-2014%2F18043&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhD2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=1025a045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-25-2014/18043</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2020"},{"pid":"62a41151e8ba6cc61665bacb7bf0635dd3966ddf","tid":2131903,"uid":21356,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:38:48.000Z","msg":"你係幫熱狗宣傳？"},{"pid":"9a007496d7c7f76f1232d4246eb4bca8bf5a1be4","tid":2131903,"uid":66260,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T07:04:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}